MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2009-1292. State ex rel. Doner v. Logan.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of relator Kuhn Farms’ application for dismissal of its claims,

It is ordered by the court that the application to dismiss is granted, and Kuhn Farms’ claims are dismissed. All other claims remain pending.

Cupp, J., not participating.
